.TH EGT 1
.SH NAME
egt \- Enrico's Getting Things Done
.SH SYNOPSIS
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B egt
is a tool to manage todo-list-and-log files scattered around the home
directory.
.SH OPTIONS
.SH EXAMPLE
To scan the home directory for egt files:
.IP
egt scan
To list projects:
.IP
egt list
To produce a weekly report:
.IP
egt weekrpt
